 corrections and interpretation of constituent ratios in marine precipitation (1986) J. Geophys. Res, 91, pp. 6647-6658; McDowell, W.H., Sanchez, C.G., Asbury, C.E., Ramos Perez, C.R., Influence of sea-salt aerosols and long range transport on precipitation chemistry at El Verde, Puerto Rico (1990) Atmospheric Environment, 24, pp. 2813-2821; Millot, R., Gaillardet, J., Dupre, B., Allegre, C.J., The global control of silicate weathering rates and the coupling with physical erosion: New insights from rivers of the Canadian Shield (2002) Earth and Planet. Sci. Lett, 196, pp. 83-98; Nakawo, M., Fujita, K., Ageta, Y., Shanker, K., Pokharel, A.P., Basic studies for assessing the impacts of the global warming on the Himalayan Cryosphere, 1994-1996 (1997) Bulletin of the Glacier Research, 15, pp. 53-58; Quade, J., English, N., DeCelles, P.G., Silicate versus carbonate weathering in the Himalaya: A comparison of the Arun and Seti river watersheds (2003) Chem. Geol, 202, pp. 275-296; Reynolds, B., Chapman, P.J., French, M.C., Jenkin, A., Wheater, H.S., Major, minor and trace element chemistry of surface waters in the Everest region Nepal (1995) Biogeochemistry of seasonally snow-covered catchments, 228, pp. 405-412. , Tonnessen K.A, M.W. Williams & M. Tranter Eds, IAHS Publ; Reynolds, R.C., Johnson, N.M., Chemical weathering in the temperate glacial environment of the Northern Cascade Mountains (1972) Geochim. Cosmochim. Acta, 36, pp. 537-554; Sakai, A., Fujita, K., Aoki, T., Asahi, K., Nakawo, M., Water discharge from the Lirung glacier in Langtang Valley, Nepal Himalaya, 1996 (1997) Bulletin of the Glacier Research, 15, pp. 79-83; Sakai, A., Takeuchi, N., Fujita, K., Nakawo, M., Role of supraglacier ponds in ablation process of a debris-covered glacier in the Nepal Himalaya (2000) IAHS, 264, pp. 119-130. , Publ. no; Sarin, M.M., Krishnaswamy, S., Trivedi, J.R., Sharma, K.K., Major ion chemistry of the Ganga source waters: Weathering in the high altitude Himalaya (1992) Proc